3ï¸âƒ£ Enable H2 Console

Add this in application.properties:

spring.h2.console.enabled=true


âœ” Restart the application
âœ” Open browser and go to:

http://localhost:8080/h2-console

4ï¸âƒ£ Problem: Dynamic H2 URL

By default, H2 generates a random URL

Every restart â†’ URL changes

This makes login difficult

5ï¸âƒ£ Solution: Configure Static H2 URL

Add this to application.properties:

