8ï¸âƒ£ Important Points to Remember

âœ… schema.sql must be in src/main/resources
âœ… Table is created automatically on startup
âœ… H2 data is lost when app stops
âœ… Static URL avoids reconnect issues

ğŸ¯ Summary

H2 is an in-memory DB

